WEBVTT

01:34.520 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:37.800 --> 01:39.640
Listen. Let's relax.

01:39.720 --> 01:41.200
- Sure thing.
- Guys, listen up.

01:41.280 --> 01:45.040
Welcome to the Nanwu High School
Alumni Association at Nanwu University.

01:45.120 --> 01:46.440
We're so distinguished

01:46.520 --> 01:49.640
that we've all realized our first choice,
Nanwu University.

01:50.280 --> 01:51.840
I suggest we raise our glasses
and make a toast.

01:51.920 --> 01:53.560
- Come on. Cheers.
- Cheers.

01:57.480 --> 01:58.320
Did anything fun happen

01:58.400 --> 01:59.240
- on the college campus?
- Let me get this.

01:59.320 --> 02:00.520
I'll go first.

02:01.040 --> 02:02.160
I'm in love.

02:02.240 --> 02:04.160
He's in love again.

02:04.240 --> 02:07.000
- What's so funny about that?
- He's been in love

02:07.080 --> 02:09.759
- since I met him in high school.
- Sang Yan.

02:11.200 --> 02:13.000
- Where are you going?
- Where are you going?

02:13.840 --> 02:14.920
Toilet. Do you need to go?

02:15.000 --> 02:16.120
Of course not.

02:16.640 --> 02:17.840
You didn't leave your house
for the whole winter vacation.

02:17.920 --> 02:19.840
I even thought you were hatching eggs.

02:19.920 --> 02:20.960
If I did, would you eat them?

02:21.040 --> 02:22.040
I don't eat your eggs.

02:23.600 --> 02:26.800
It's not often we go out and have fun.
Don't get all uptight about it, okay?

02:27.480 --> 02:29.440
No. I haven't shown you
my girlfriend's photos yet.

02:29.520 --> 02:30.680
Come on.

02:30.760 --> 02:31.880
Do you want to see
my girlfriend's picture?

02:31.960 --> 02:33.320
Come on. We all want that.

02:33.400 --> 02:35.240
Let's see it together.

02:35.320 --> 02:36.640
Come back to me later.

02:36.720 --> 02:39.120
- Come on. Come on, guys. Everybody.
- Let me see.

02:40.200 --> 02:41.880
Are you really not
coming back for winter vacation?

02:42.400 --> 02:45.520
I was hoping you'd come to Nanwu
or I'd go to Beiyu to meet you.

02:46.600 --> 02:48.640
Why don't you come back?

02:50.120 --> 02:51.080
Are you in love?

02:52.120 --> 02:53.000
Wen Yifan.

02:53.080 --> 02:55.880
If you're in love,
you have to tell me, you know?

02:55.960 --> 02:57.520
Are you really my best friend?

02:58.240 --> 03:00.400
But why don't you come back?

03:00.480 --> 03:02.920
How pathetic for you to have
the Spring Festival alone there.

03:03.000 --> 03:03.840
By the way,

03:03.920 --> 03:06.200
I've downloaded that handheld game
you asked me to download last time,

03:06.280 --> 03:09.120
but I forgot
which server you said last time.

03:09.200 --> 03:10.040
Unrivaled?

03:11.880 --> 03:12.960
Then I didn't misremember.

03:13.800 --> 03:15.960
But why did you suddenly
start playing games?

03:16.480 --> 03:17.840
By the way, what's your ID?

03:17.920 --> 03:19.480
I'm going to make up
an ID similar to yours.

03:19.560 --> 03:21.840
Warm Water?

03:22.880 --> 03:23.840
Then, what ID should I have?

03:23.920 --> 03:27.080
It'll be Fierce Ice Water.

03:33.320 --> 03:34.840
SYNOPSIS

03:34.920 --> 03:37.600
DRAGON PRINCE

03:37.680 --> 03:39.200
XUAN CAI'E

03:41.000 --> 03:42.280
What's your ID?

03:42.360 --> 03:44.240
I'm going to make up
an ID similar to yours.

03:46.520 --> 03:51.480
COMPARISON OF MAGIC SCHOOLS

03:51.560 --> 03:53.440
BAI JIANG

04:08.680 --> 04:10.160
3,411 DAYS

04:11.520 --> 04:14.800
DAY 1 OF FALLING IN LOVE

04:14.880 --> 04:16.120
I'm at my hotel.

04:19.920 --> 04:23.040
It's so late, so you probably
won't be able to get a ticket back.

04:26.000 --> 04:27.760
Do you want to stay here tonight?

04:30.880 --> 04:33.560
I mean, I'll book you a room
on the same floor as mine.

04:36.200 --> 04:37.320
Okay.

04:42.000 --> 04:42.960
This is it.

04:47.000 --> 04:49.600
Your room should be the one furthest in.

04:50.480 --> 04:51.520
Take me there.

04:58.680 --> 05:00.080
It's so far from yours.

05:05.360 --> 05:06.880
I'm going back to my room now.

05:07.400 --> 05:09.080
Do you have other work to do?

05:12.000 --> 05:13.440
Anything else to do?

05:15.000 --> 05:16.840
- No.
- Then why are you going back?

05:21.440 --> 05:22.840
Does he want me to go into his room?

05:23.880 --> 05:25.160
Go in by yourself.

05:39.680 --> 05:41.840
We've just fallen in love,

05:41.920 --> 05:44.520
so I'm afraid you'll be upset
if I enter your personal space.

05:45.520 --> 05:47.840
That sounds like something
a decent guy would say,

05:48.360 --> 05:50.680
but who would've guessed
you've already touched me all over?

05:56.320 --> 05:57.640
What happened to your job?

05:58.440 --> 06:00.440
You lost all the weight
I spent so long helping you gain

06:00.520 --> 06:02.240
in half a month.

06:15.520 --> 06:17.840
What's going on? What happened?

06:20.880 --> 06:23.200
I cut myself on some gravel.
It's not serious.

06:25.560 --> 06:28.280
Really not. I just got cut by accident.

06:31.360 --> 06:33.320
By the way, why did you come to Beiyu?

06:34.240 --> 06:35.720
Didn't I say I'd go back tomorrow?

06:36.320 --> 06:39.200
Also, did you get the cake I ordered?

06:39.280 --> 06:40.600
I came to get my birthday present.

06:42.440 --> 06:44.440
I left your birthday present at home.

06:48.160 --> 06:49.480
I'll give it to you tomorrow
when I get back.

06:51.040 --> 06:52.280
Okay.

06:55.720 --> 06:57.200
Can you help me find my cell phone?

07:07.640 --> 07:09.400
Did you leave it
at the noodle restaurant? It's…

07:48.600 --> 07:49.600
Thank you.

07:52.400 --> 07:53.400
I've received it.

08:01.960 --> 08:04.240
It's here. We don't have to look for it.

08:07.880 --> 08:09.200
I'll wash the apples.

08:17.880 --> 08:18.920
Wen Shuangjiang.

08:21.400 --> 08:22.640
After all these years,

08:25.360 --> 08:26.360
I still

08:28.920 --> 08:29.800
only love you.

08:57.840 --> 08:59.880
Hello. Your pizza.

08:59.960 --> 09:02.160
PIZZA HUT

09:04.800 --> 09:06.320
- Here's yours. Three servings.
- Thank you.

09:06.400 --> 09:07.760
Enjoy your meal.

09:10.720 --> 09:13.280
So many takeaways. Are you hungry?

09:14.120 --> 09:15.920
I just don't want you to be hungry.

09:26.400 --> 09:28.760
I'll finish my apple later
and go back to my room.

09:40.200 --> 09:41.240
Won't you eat?

09:43.600 --> 09:44.560
I will.

09:46.160 --> 09:49.840
So, can we eat the pizza a little slower?

09:56.080 --> 09:57.560
Is half an hour enough?

09:59.840 --> 10:02.400
Can we go slower than that?

10:50.040 --> 10:51.440
The rain seems to have stopped.

10:56.280 --> 10:59.120
By the way, when did you buy the tickets?

10:59.200 --> 11:01.320
Actually,

11:01.400 --> 11:03.720
I wanted to buy tickets to go back today
for your birthday,

11:03.800 --> 11:04.840
but they were sold out.

11:08.040 --> 11:08.880
Last week.

11:08.960 --> 11:11.480
Did you know last week
that I couldn't get back today?

11:11.560 --> 11:14.560
No, but just in case.

11:16.000 --> 11:17.080
Then I'll do the same later.

11:21.360 --> 11:22.840
I'm going back.

11:23.600 --> 11:25.040
I have to get up early
tomorrow and go back.

11:25.120 --> 11:26.800
I'll stop chatting. Good night.

11:32.960 --> 11:34.000
Sang Yan.

11:35.720 --> 11:36.640
What?

11:39.800 --> 11:40.800
Happy birthday.

11:45.520 --> 11:46.960
What's your birthday wish?

11:51.440 --> 11:53.320
- I won't say.
- Why not?

11:55.160 --> 11:57.800
Because it's already come true.

12:08.760 --> 12:09.640
Good night.

12:23.760 --> 12:25.080
QIAO

12:25.160 --> 12:27.360
Did you see that?
Sang Yan posted in his WeChat Moment.

12:29.120 --> 12:30.800
He has a girlfriend.

12:31.400 --> 12:33.880
You didn't say anything,
so his girlfriend must not be you.

12:33.960 --> 12:34.920
Then who is it?

12:35.000 --> 12:37.200
He doesn't even tell us when he's in love.

12:37.280 --> 12:39.160
Luckily, you didn't have
anything with him.

12:39.240 --> 12:41.400
Did his account get hacked?

12:41.480 --> 12:44.320
That's too much.
Take a look at the screenshot I sent you.

12:46.640 --> 12:47.840
SANG YAN

12:47.920 --> 12:49.840
DUAN JIAXU
HAS YOUR ACCOUNT BEEN HACKED?

12:49.920 --> 12:52.040
SANG YAN: SORRY
MY GIRLFRIEND ASKED ME TO POST

12:53.320 --> 12:54.440
So he got the cake.

12:59.280 --> 13:02.000
HE WASN'T HACKED

13:03.520 --> 13:04.960
HIS GIRLFRIEND IS ME

13:23.800 --> 13:25.160
- Hello?
- Hello?

13:25.240 --> 13:27.000
Dian. What's going on?

13:27.080 --> 13:30.240
Just like what I said.
It happened just now.

13:30.320 --> 13:33.000
Aren't you on a business trip?
How do you have time for that?

13:33.080 --> 13:35.480
And didn't you say before
that you weren't getting anywhere?

13:36.520 --> 13:37.920
- Did I?
- Yes.

13:38.000 --> 13:42.320
You caused me to worry about you two.
You're such a lukewarm character.

13:42.400 --> 13:45.160
Tell me. How did it go so fast?

13:46.640 --> 13:48.560
Probably because I didn't control myself.

13:49.640 --> 13:52.160
Gosh. Wen Yifan.

13:52.240 --> 13:53.400
When are you going back to Nanwu?

13:54.000 --> 13:56.240
- Tomorrow morning.
- Then we'll meet at noon.

13:56.320 --> 13:57.480
Talk me through it.

13:57.560 --> 13:58.680
Okay, then.

13:58.760 --> 14:00.360
That's it. Bye.

14:09.920 --> 14:12.920
GRANDPA LOVES WOODIE JR. THANK YOU

14:15.120 --> 14:16.760
Are you really my friend?

14:16.840 --> 14:20.160
You're either stalking me
or not replying to me for so long.

14:20.680 --> 14:24.040
How are you and your grandpa doing?
You need to check in with me.

14:36.400 --> 14:38.880
I didn't message back for so long because…

14:41.440 --> 14:42.280
Because…

14:45.120 --> 14:46.920
Sorry. I'm a little nervous.

14:47.000 --> 14:48.200
It's because

14:49.480 --> 14:50.720
I don't want to be just friends with you.

14:55.920 --> 14:57.840
I want to be your boyfriend, okay?

15:01.760 --> 15:03.280
Just confess like that?

15:05.840 --> 15:08.080
I'm next to your house right now.

15:08.960 --> 15:10.400
Anhe Bridge.

15:30.480 --> 15:31.520
Xiang Lang?

15:33.440 --> 15:34.560
Why are you here?

15:34.640 --> 15:35.760
I just wanted to call you.

15:35.840 --> 15:38.200
I just got off the plane
and wanted to surprise you.

15:38.720 --> 15:40.720
We're on vacation at work,
so I wanted to come back and see you guys.

15:45.280 --> 15:46.800
It's a bit of a shock.

15:46.880 --> 15:48.680
Why not a surprise but a shock?

15:48.760 --> 15:51.880
Actually, it just so happens
that a friend came to see me, too.

15:51.960 --> 15:53.520
Meeting you this late?

15:56.920 --> 15:58.880
- Dian?
- No.

15:58.960 --> 16:01.600
It's a boy.

16:03.000 --> 16:05.080
Don't think too much. You know him, too.

16:05.160 --> 16:06.080
I know him, too?

16:08.280 --> 16:09.840
So, can we go together?

16:12.120 --> 16:14.040
Maybe… OK.

16:22.120 --> 16:24.640
I've just learned some very shocking news.

16:25.480 --> 16:27.040
I think you'll know it sooner or later.

16:27.560 --> 16:31.160
Dian is in love with Sang Yan.

16:36.560 --> 16:38.800
But that's good. We should wish them well.

16:40.400 --> 16:41.560
Are you sure you're okay?

16:42.440 --> 16:43.480
Of course.

16:44.360 --> 16:47.400
What about you?
When can you care about yourself?

16:49.200 --> 16:50.200
I…

17:12.520 --> 17:15.119
I'm sorry to bother you…

17:16.160 --> 17:17.079
guys.

17:20.119 --> 17:21.880
You're the one who asked Qiao out so late.

17:21.960 --> 17:23.160
You're together?

17:25.079 --> 17:28.600
What a coincidence.
He's here to see me too.

17:29.120 --> 17:31.240
Yes. I just came back
from Hong Kong, China,

17:31.320 --> 17:32.520
to meet my childhood friend.

17:33.560 --> 17:35.000
Actually,

17:35.840 --> 17:37.600
I have something important
to talk to Qiao alone today,

17:38.720 --> 17:39.960
but I didn't expect you to be here.

17:40.040 --> 17:41.320
But that's okay.

17:41.400 --> 17:44.200
As a man, I don't need to hide anything.

17:44.720 --> 17:45.560
Zhong Siqiao.

17:46.840 --> 17:49.000
- I want you to be my--
- Wait.

17:49.080 --> 17:51.440
Don't be impulsive. Let's talk privately.

17:51.520 --> 17:53.720
- What's so bad about this?
- Qiao.

17:54.480 --> 17:55.680
Let him say.

17:55.760 --> 17:56.800
But…

17:58.560 --> 18:00.880
Don't care about me.
Grab your own happiness.

18:01.480 --> 18:03.320
- Su Haoan, I just feel--
- Xiang Lang.

18:03.400 --> 18:04.280
What do you mean?

18:05.240 --> 18:06.680
I think you may have misunderstood.

18:06.760 --> 18:09.160
Qiao and I will always be best friends,

18:09.760 --> 18:12.120
so, Su Haoan,
if you want to say something,

18:13.040 --> 18:13.880
just say it.

18:17.800 --> 18:19.920
Xiang Lang, don't you love Wen Yifan?

18:21.320 --> 18:22.280
I made it very clear just now.

18:25.960 --> 18:27.640
So, you've rejected
Zhong Siqiao's confession?

18:27.720 --> 18:28.600
Yes.

18:28.680 --> 18:30.480
I confessed to Xiang Lang, but he refused.

18:30.560 --> 18:32.320
That was my wishful thinking, okay?

18:32.400 --> 18:33.880
Both of you, stop it, okay?

18:33.960 --> 18:36.480
- You still love him, don't you?
- Of course not. How can that be?

18:36.560 --> 18:39.960
- Then, why don't you try to accept me?
- How can I try?

18:46.040 --> 18:47.480
So, it was my wishful thinking.

18:48.600 --> 18:50.480
I'm sorry to bother you.

18:53.120 --> 18:54.320
Su Haoan.

19:11.160 --> 19:13.680
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

19:15.160 --> 19:16.680
We're going to meet downstairs

19:16.760 --> 19:18.720
and probably have breakfast
before going back.

19:18.800 --> 19:19.640
Okay.

19:21.000 --> 19:21.840
Did you sleep well?

19:29.240 --> 19:30.280
Let's go.

19:32.520 --> 19:33.720
Are you coming with us?

19:35.640 --> 19:36.520
Can't I?

20:19.640 --> 20:21.640
- Hi. Check out.
- Hi.

20:21.720 --> 20:23.560
- Me too.
- Okay. Just a moment.

20:25.400 --> 20:27.360
Ma'am. Confirm check-out.

20:28.640 --> 20:31.040
- Morning, Ms. Qian.
- Done.

20:33.400 --> 20:34.240
It's you.

20:35.480 --> 20:37.640
Are you here for work or pleasure?

20:37.720 --> 20:38.760
I'm here to see her.

20:40.800 --> 20:41.840
Let's go check out.

20:42.880 --> 20:43.880
Okay.

20:43.960 --> 20:45.800
Check out for me.
I need to confirm something.

20:49.320 --> 20:50.480
Sang Yan.

20:51.040 --> 20:53.040
I know you want to see Yifan,

20:53.120 --> 20:56.760
but I'm afraid it's not right for you
to follow her even when she's traveling.

20:58.120 --> 20:59.640
Yifan has a good personality,

21:00.240 --> 21:02.360
so she won't get mad at you,

21:02.440 --> 21:04.840
but you have to think
about her feelings a bit.

21:16.160 --> 21:19.480
You're courting her like this.
No wonder it doesn't work.

21:20.160 --> 21:21.840
It just puts pressure on her.

21:29.000 --> 21:30.080
We're long past that stage.

21:31.320 --> 21:32.720
Have you got everything?

21:32.800 --> 21:34.240
We are now having

21:34.320 --> 21:38.000
mutual feelings.

21:39.440 --> 21:41.720
Ever heard that phrase?

21:46.160 --> 21:48.760
Have you? Who said that?

21:49.680 --> 21:51.960
- Me.
- I'm glad you admit it.

21:53.600 --> 21:54.840
NEWS REPORTING VEHICLE

21:54.920 --> 21:56.600
Ms. Qian. Let me drive.

21:56.680 --> 21:58.680
- Take a break.
- It's okay.

21:58.760 --> 22:01.480
I've been up so late these days
that my bones almost fell apart.

22:01.560 --> 22:02.840
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

22:03.360 --> 22:04.200
I'm sorry.

22:04.280 --> 22:06.440
I'm supposed to drive,
but I don't have a license.

22:08.080 --> 22:10.160
- Let me help you.
- Thank you.

22:11.120 --> 22:14.000
- I'll drive.
- Didn't you take a cab?

22:16.760 --> 22:17.800
Give me directions.

22:21.360 --> 22:23.280
But we have to get
to the TV station first.

22:23.360 --> 22:24.360
All right. Get in the car.

22:37.680 --> 22:38.600
Qiao.

22:40.000 --> 22:42.200
- Sorry to keep you waiting.
- Dian.

22:42.720 --> 22:45.560
Xiang Lang. When did you come back?

22:45.640 --> 22:46.480
Not long ago.

22:53.400 --> 22:54.440
What happened to you?

22:55.680 --> 22:57.440
I didn't sleep well last night.

22:58.720 --> 23:00.160
Is it because of me?

23:02.120 --> 23:04.680
You don't have to keep your voice down.
I've already accidentally let him know.

23:05.800 --> 23:07.000
Besides,

23:07.080 --> 23:09.160
I'm very happy
that you're in love with Sang Yan.

23:09.240 --> 23:10.320
So, what happened to you?

23:13.160 --> 23:14.760
Yesterday,

23:14.840 --> 23:17.440
I happened to bump into Su Haoan
confessing his love to Qiao,

23:17.520 --> 23:20.000
but he was ruthlessly rejected by Qiao.

23:20.640 --> 23:22.080
Su Haoan was almost crashed.

23:24.120 --> 23:26.000
Really? Su Haoan?

23:27.080 --> 23:28.440
You think it's
unbelievable too, don't you?

23:29.280 --> 23:30.520
He loves you?

23:31.200 --> 23:32.320
Do you love him?

23:34.600 --> 23:35.560
I don't know,

23:36.320 --> 23:38.040
but when I don't see him,

23:38.120 --> 23:40.800
I'll wonder
why I can't hear from him at all.

23:41.320 --> 23:42.800
And yet, as soon as we met…

23:42.880 --> 23:44.240
He confessed to her.

23:45.400 --> 23:48.480
Anyway, when I met him,
all sorts of strange things happened.

23:48.560 --> 23:51.720
So, maybe it's a kind of fate.

23:53.720 --> 23:54.720
No way.

23:54.800 --> 23:56.760
We're not even the same species on Earth.

23:57.960 --> 24:01.280
You're always the professional
when guiding me in my relationships.

24:01.800 --> 24:03.840
- How is this the same?
- That's enough.

24:03.920 --> 24:06.280
Su Haoan seems a little mindless,

24:06.360 --> 24:07.920
but I think

24:08.440 --> 24:10.720
he's quite affectionate and dedicated.

24:10.800 --> 24:12.440
You're different from him.

24:12.520 --> 24:13.800
You seem to have a big heart

24:13.880 --> 24:16.320
but a lot of worries.

24:16.400 --> 24:17.840
Don't you complement each other?

24:19.200 --> 24:20.080
Don't you want to give it a try?

24:21.680 --> 24:23.760
Forget it. I won't. Let's eat.

24:24.280 --> 24:25.120
Okay.

24:27.920 --> 24:30.760
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

24:30.840 --> 24:31.880
Home at last.

24:58.480 --> 24:59.480
Aren't you forgetting something?

25:07.440 --> 25:08.400
Just give me a second.

25:52.160 --> 25:53.120
A coat?

26:16.760 --> 26:18.280
Why this color?

26:18.920 --> 26:21.840
Because I haven't seen you
wear this color.

26:21.920 --> 26:23.120
I feel it suits you.

26:27.440 --> 26:28.760
Your hat.

26:36.280 --> 26:37.520
You don't like it?

26:38.040 --> 26:39.840
Then I'll give you another present.

26:41.560 --> 26:42.720
Who says I don't like it?

26:44.920 --> 26:46.720
I've received quite a few gifts this year.

26:47.560 --> 26:49.520
In terms of satisfaction,

26:52.440 --> 26:53.400
this one can be ranked second.

26:54.640 --> 26:55.840
And what's number one?

26:58.400 --> 27:00.200
- The one I got yesterday.
- What's that?

27:00.280 --> 27:01.280
What do you think?

27:04.200 --> 27:05.400
Let me guess.

27:14.520 --> 27:15.760
Thank you.

27:23.400 --> 27:24.560
As long as you like it.

27:29.680 --> 27:30.800
Stop thinking.

27:32.560 --> 27:33.600
You're number one.

27:41.240 --> 27:42.080
What's wrong?

27:44.560 --> 27:45.440
Did you put the medicine on?

27:47.520 --> 27:48.360
It scabbed over.

27:57.960 --> 27:59.080
It's really not that bad.

27:59.840 --> 28:01.920
This thing will heal naturally.

28:04.480 --> 28:06.560
The atmosphere's a little gritty,

28:06.640 --> 28:09.240
so I've got to think of a way
to keep him from being serious.

28:19.080 --> 28:20.120
It hurts.

28:23.640 --> 28:25.680
Are you blackmailing me?
Why so far away from me?

28:32.720 --> 28:33.600
Come over a little.

28:38.120 --> 28:39.640
Don't take liberties with me by that.

28:42.560 --> 28:43.720
I'll be careful.

28:46.680 --> 28:49.000
Can you control your force?

28:51.120 --> 28:53.040
Do journalists have to learn acting?

28:56.920 --> 28:58.800
Actually, I didn't care much
about the wound after it scabbed over.

28:58.880 --> 29:00.360
I thought it was almost healed.

29:00.440 --> 29:02.920
So, you guys always get hurt on the job?

29:12.160 --> 29:13.000
Now it doesn't hurt?

29:17.280 --> 29:19.600
All right. Go get some rest.

29:29.400 --> 29:30.960
Come back to me tomorrow after your bath.

29:39.600 --> 29:40.680
Isn't this too soon?

29:46.440 --> 29:49.120
What are you thinking about?
I'm going to put medicine on you.

30:21.480 --> 30:23.400
Yifan, let's go.

30:33.360 --> 30:34.480
Yifan.

30:36.320 --> 30:38.560
Fu Zhuang, excuse me.
Let me take her a few minutes.

30:38.640 --> 30:40.840
- Yifan, I'll wait for you in the car.
- OK.

30:42.080 --> 30:42.920
What's wrong?

30:47.400 --> 30:48.480
I don't understand

30:48.560 --> 30:51.000
why you're in love with Sang Yan.

30:51.600 --> 30:53.360
I really can't find
anything good about him.

30:53.440 --> 30:56.400
Why do you have to compromise yourself?

30:57.520 --> 30:58.360
I didn't.

31:00.400 --> 31:01.720
Has he ever tried to confess to you?

31:10.560 --> 31:12.520
He cares about me like
he's confessing to me every day.

31:12.600 --> 31:14.120
Can he be like that?

31:16.200 --> 31:17.040
I don't care.

31:17.800 --> 31:20.200
If he dares to break your heart,

31:20.720 --> 31:22.040
I can get back at him hard for you.

31:24.640 --> 31:26.040
Okay. Thanks.

31:30.600 --> 31:33.640
Actually, I've been in love with him
since high school.

31:33.720 --> 31:35.200
I just never admitted it.

31:40.080 --> 31:42.040
I feel happy to be in love

31:44.000 --> 31:45.240
with him now.

31:46.200 --> 31:47.080
OK.

31:47.600 --> 31:50.160
You'll meet someone
who cherishes you in the future.

31:51.120 --> 31:52.240
I'm going to work.

32:01.840 --> 32:02.760
Here's the dish.

32:04.560 --> 32:05.480
Main course.

32:05.560 --> 32:06.520
Fish in muddy water.

32:07.560 --> 32:08.600
What are you doing?

32:09.120 --> 32:10.000
Serving.

32:10.080 --> 32:11.000
EATING TOFU JELLY

32:12.560 --> 32:15.160
- Taste it.
- What's the plan for after dinner?

32:15.680 --> 32:17.400
NOTHING YET

32:18.680 --> 32:19.600
Then come to Overtime.

32:21.680 --> 32:24.040
AREN'T YOU PARTYING WITH THEM?

32:25.720 --> 32:27.360
It's so boring. Be with me.

32:32.320 --> 32:34.360
- We'll be right there.
- Where are we going?

32:35.160 --> 32:36.800
- To Overtime.
- Let's go.

32:45.560 --> 32:48.000
Do they know you're in love with Sang Yan?

32:48.520 --> 32:51.200
Probably not. I didn't ask.

32:51.280 --> 32:54.080
Since you're already in love,
ask if you want to.

32:54.680 --> 32:55.560
Wait.

32:55.640 --> 32:58.200
Feel my heartbeat.
Why is it racing? I'm so nervous.

32:58.280 --> 32:59.720
Why are you nervous?

33:00.240 --> 33:02.720
Please. This will be the first time

33:02.800 --> 33:04.640
Sang Yan appeared in front of me
as my best friend's boyfriend.

33:04.720 --> 33:06.320
I don't even know how to face him.

33:06.840 --> 33:07.680
Let me see where he is.

33:13.040 --> 33:14.600
Just do the same as before.

33:16.240 --> 33:17.160
OK.

33:19.840 --> 33:21.080
Indeed,

33:21.160 --> 33:25.640
I'm also a bit overwhelmed by the change
in our relationship after so many years.

33:33.000 --> 33:34.360
Taste what I just cooked today.

33:35.120 --> 33:36.640
Taste the fish in muddy water.

33:41.240 --> 33:42.120
- There you are.
- Hello.

33:42.200 --> 33:43.000
- There you are.
- Hello.

33:43.080 --> 33:43.800
- Welcome.
- Hello.

33:43.880 --> 33:44.920
- Sit down.
- Come on.

33:45.000 --> 33:46.640
Come on.

33:46.720 --> 33:47.960
- Come on, Yifan. Sit next to me.
- Thank you.

33:48.040 --> 33:49.000
Here. Use this.

33:50.480 --> 33:51.520
Thank you.

33:54.840 --> 33:56.400
What are you doing?

33:56.480 --> 33:58.800
- What do you mean?
- Thanks.

33:58.880 --> 34:00.840
Don't you have a girlfriend?

34:00.920 --> 34:02.800
Why do you invite other girls
to sit next to you?

34:02.880 --> 34:04.000
Don't ask.

34:08.239 --> 34:10.400
Looks like he hasn't told them yet.

34:14.440 --> 34:15.520
- Why are you looking at me?
- It's the first time

34:15.600 --> 34:16.480
I've seen you in khaki.

34:16.560 --> 34:18.960
No wonder
l felt something strange about Yan today.

34:19.040 --> 34:20.960
It's so obvious,
but you're just now realizing it?

34:21.040 --> 34:22.480
What's the point of wearing this?

34:22.560 --> 34:24.960
It's so flirty.
Are you the hero of a movie?

34:25.040 --> 34:26.159
Right, Yifan?

34:26.880 --> 34:28.000
Right?

34:28.679 --> 34:30.000
Maybe.

34:30.760 --> 34:32.120
I think it's quite manly.

34:32.639 --> 34:33.679
You don't have an aesthetic.

34:34.280 --> 34:36.080
My girlfriend bought it for me.

34:36.159 --> 34:37.239
She likes this color.

34:38.199 --> 34:39.159
Girlfriend?

34:39.679 --> 34:40.600
Oh my God.

34:41.120 --> 34:43.440
You're moving too fast
with your girlfriend.

34:43.520 --> 34:45.280
How long have you been in love?

34:45.360 --> 34:47.719
- You called her girlfriend.
- Wine.

34:48.400 --> 34:49.320
- Thank you.
- Looking good.

34:49.400 --> 34:50.239
Thank you.

34:50.320 --> 34:51.520
Come on. Taste it.

34:52.239 --> 34:53.239
She doesn't drink.

34:53.960 --> 34:55.679
- Right?
- Sang Yan.

34:55.760 --> 34:58.920
We've been sitting here all afternoon,
and you haven't had a drink,

34:59.440 --> 35:00.880
but now you're taking Yifan's.

35:00.960 --> 35:02.360
I don't drink either. I'm going to drive.

35:02.440 --> 35:04.200
Sang Yan, you're so weird,

35:04.280 --> 35:08.520
but I have to kindly remind you,
who's been single since birth,

35:08.600 --> 35:10.520
- not to be like me.
- Don't worry. I won't.

35:10.600 --> 35:11.680
Yan.

35:12.680 --> 35:14.240
I'd also like to remind you

35:15.040 --> 35:16.600
to restrain yourself

35:17.640 --> 35:18.720
so you won't scare away

35:18.800 --> 35:22.200
the only woman in the world
who can put up with your bad temper.

35:22.720 --> 35:23.800
It's not sure
if he has a girlfriend or not.

35:25.520 --> 35:26.520
OK.

35:26.600 --> 35:28.480
I won't be like you either.

35:28.560 --> 35:30.160
Can I be a backup like you or…

35:31.520 --> 35:32.880
She only likes people like me.

35:33.920 --> 35:36.440
So, when are you gonna
bring your girlfriend over

35:36.520 --> 35:38.840
and show us? Right?

35:38.920 --> 35:40.200
How many days has it been?

35:40.280 --> 35:41.800
Or are you so unsure

35:41.880 --> 35:43.040
that you're afraid your girlfriend
will fall in love with me

35:43.120 --> 35:44.200
when she gets here?

35:45.960 --> 35:47.280
Stop bragging. It's a pipe dream.

35:48.360 --> 35:50.120
- See you later.
- Look. He's gone again.

35:50.200 --> 35:51.040
- Nonsense.
- Bye-bye.

35:51.120 --> 35:52.160
Bye.

35:53.760 --> 35:55.200
Come on, Yifan.

35:58.440 --> 35:59.360
- Are you leaving, too?
- You're going, too?

35:59.440 --> 36:01.720
With him? No. Come back. Sit down.

36:01.800 --> 36:03.640
- Don't go.
- Sang Yan.

36:03.720 --> 36:05.560
You have a girlfriend,

36:05.640 --> 36:08.160
but why do you still hang out
with your roommate every day?

36:08.240 --> 36:09.880
What's the matter with you?

36:09.960 --> 36:11.920
Is your girlfriend okay with this?

36:12.000 --> 36:14.440
- It's inappropriate.
- Think about it.

36:14.960 --> 36:17.080
Two idiots.

36:17.600 --> 36:18.640
- See you later.
- Just go.

36:18.720 --> 36:19.720
- Qiao.
- Don't worry about me.

36:19.800 --> 36:21.080
- Qiao, don't go.
- I won't.

36:21.160 --> 36:22.600
- Stay here.
- Don't get too close.

36:23.120 --> 36:24.280
- Yeah.
- Come on. Let's drink.

36:24.360 --> 36:25.680
- Come on.
- Try my new dish.

36:25.760 --> 36:27.800
- OK.
- Come on.

36:27.880 --> 36:30.560
Didn't you tell them
I was your girlfriend?

36:31.720 --> 36:34.000
I didn't think they'd be able to tell.

36:35.360 --> 36:37.520
I'd better tell them in a formal setting.

36:39.080 --> 36:40.200
What? You can't wait?

36:41.160 --> 36:43.080
I'm just curious.

36:46.000 --> 36:48.440
- Is this coat really nice?
- Of course.

36:48.960 --> 36:51.280
Both the shape and the fabric.

36:51.800 --> 36:53.680
And it's very warm, too.
I'm even sweating.

36:56.000 --> 37:00.560
I was going to say that this color
might make you look a little softer,

37:01.080 --> 37:02.960
- but I didn't expect…
- Didn't expect what?

37:03.840 --> 37:07.280
I didn't expect it
to be as cocky as you are.

37:09.480 --> 37:11.920
What? Shocked by how handsome
your boyfriend is?

37:14.040 --> 37:15.320
Whatever you say.

37:16.480 --> 37:17.360
Have dinner with me.

37:18.040 --> 37:20.680
- Didn't you eat just now?
- No. I was waiting for you.

37:25.280 --> 37:26.280
Have you eaten?

37:26.800 --> 37:27.800
A little.

37:29.880 --> 37:31.680
Didn't I just show you a picture?

37:49.040 --> 37:50.080
What do you mean?

37:50.600 --> 37:53.840
Are you settling a score with me
or to show your hand to your rival?

37:54.600 --> 37:55.640
Sit down and talk.

38:05.120 --> 38:06.160
Have some water.

38:09.080 --> 38:11.200
I know you're busy, so I'm sorry,

38:12.880 --> 38:15.360
but I really don't know who to talk to.

38:15.440 --> 38:19.280
I had a really hard time before.
I've never felt this way before.

38:20.320 --> 38:22.320
I just want to know more about her.

38:22.400 --> 38:23.680
Of course, I wanted
to ask Wen Yifan at first,

38:25.280 --> 38:29.320
but I felt that Qiao would be angry
if she knew,

38:29.400 --> 38:30.560
so after thinking it over,

38:31.440 --> 38:33.520
I asked you to come here.

38:36.880 --> 38:38.040
Actually,

38:39.920 --> 38:42.560
Qiao wasn't as happy as she seemed,

38:43.080 --> 38:45.960
but she always played along
without saying anything.

38:46.880 --> 38:49.240
When she was a sophomore in high school,

38:51.160 --> 38:53.080
Dian moved to Beiyu.

38:53.160 --> 38:55.280
Actually, she was never happy
during that time.

38:55.800 --> 38:58.520
When I came back to see her
during my first winter break,

38:58.600 --> 39:01.520
she didn't accept that right away.

39:02.320 --> 39:03.600
It was very unlike her before.

39:04.480 --> 39:06.480
I expected you
to extort a big meal from me,

39:06.560 --> 39:08.200
but I didn't expect you
to treat me to a cake.

39:08.280 --> 39:09.400
Why don't you eat it?

39:10.280 --> 39:13.520
I suddenly feel that the three of us
have become so distant.

39:14.800 --> 39:16.200
Nanwu Trio?

39:16.280 --> 39:17.840
No one even cares about that.

39:20.000 --> 39:23.200
What's wrong with you?
Did something happen to you recently?

39:24.960 --> 39:26.560
Do things have to happen to me
to make me miss you?

39:26.640 --> 39:30.440
Do friends have to care about each other
when something happens to them?

39:33.720 --> 39:36.040
We've all been a little busy lately.

39:37.760 --> 39:38.760
Yes.

39:39.880 --> 39:40.880
You're all busy.

39:41.480 --> 39:43.240
You don't have to make time

39:43.320 --> 39:46.160
to see me during the short time
you're here.

39:54.200 --> 39:56.720
Qiao. I'm sorry.

39:58.440 --> 40:00.120
Do you know why I bought the cake?

40:00.920 --> 40:04.160
Because you're going back soon.
Your birthday is on March 14th.

40:04.240 --> 40:06.280
I was worried no one
would celebrate your birthday there,

40:06.360 --> 40:07.760
so I bought it.

40:08.720 --> 40:10.800
I remember your
and Dian's birthday every year,

40:10.880 --> 40:12.560
but what about you guys?
Do you remember mine?

40:17.320 --> 40:20.120
She always remembers what everyone likes

40:21.360 --> 40:22.720
and our birthdays.

40:24.160 --> 40:27.680
It's like we're all used
to her being there.

40:29.680 --> 40:32.240
She's often not the one at the center,

40:32.760 --> 40:36.040
but the one at the center sure needs her.

40:43.120 --> 40:46.240
Can you tell me more?

40:50.440 --> 40:52.640
Would you like some? Talk while eating.

40:57.520 --> 41:01.080
I just feel like I don't know
anything about her,

41:01.160 --> 41:04.160
so I'd like to learn more about her.

41:06.920 --> 41:08.840
I thought of one more thing.

41:10.800 --> 41:12.200
Actually, during that time,

41:12.280 --> 41:14.400
it wasn't all because of Dian
that she was unhappy.

41:15.400 --> 41:18.840
At that time, her mom and dad
were about to be divorced.

41:25.440 --> 41:27.880
Which flavor of dumpling would you like?

41:30.160 --> 41:32.240
Or do you want to order something else?

41:33.440 --> 41:35.240
Take your pick. I owe you a meal anyway.

41:37.160 --> 41:38.360
But this one doesn't count.

41:42.160 --> 41:44.280
You decide. What do you want to eat?

41:44.800 --> 41:46.120
Don't you have a lot of taboos?

41:49.240 --> 41:50.360
Not anymore.

41:51.920 --> 41:52.960
What are you looking at?

41:55.200 --> 41:56.360
That lamp is pretty.

41:57.960 --> 41:59.000
Now eat.

42:03.160 --> 42:04.440
Do you like it?

42:04.960 --> 42:07.400
I ordered something with strong flavors.

42:10.400 --> 42:11.520
Do you like it?

42:12.400 --> 42:13.560
Don't you like mild food?

42:15.160 --> 42:17.720
I tried to imagine what you like.

42:24.520 --> 42:26.200
I do like dumplings quite a bit.

42:31.800 --> 42:32.800
What are you looking at?

42:35.040 --> 42:35.960
The ferris wheel.

42:39.000 --> 42:41.000
Let's eat quickly then.

42:41.520 --> 42:43.440
When we're done, let's go there.

43:05.240 --> 43:06.920
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

43:07.000 --> 43:09.400
- Hello, sir. The things you want.
- Thank you.

43:27.280 --> 43:29.280
What are you looking at? This is mine.

43:53.400 --> 43:55.400
SANG YAN, HAPPY BIRTHDAY!

46:44.160 --> 46:45.000
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

46:45.080 --> 46:45.920
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
